==Description== <!--T:2-->

<!--T:8-->
The '''TechDraw LeaderLine''' tool adds a line to a View. Other annotation objects (such as [[TechDraw_RichTextAnnotation|Rich Text Annotations]]) can be connected to the leaderline to form complex annotations. 

